title: Birth Of Joy "Dead Being Alive" - Converse Red Light Sessions
description: Plenty of fuzz and energy as Dutch Blues Rockers Birth Of Joy made a stop at the Red Light Radio pop-up studio in Austin Texas during their USA tour.
